window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Once the Rift Magus, I was reborn as Lucian Eldraine, with my knowledge intact but my strength greatly diminished. Through trials and effort, I quickly reclaimed some of my lost powers—and even found some that were new.</b></p> <p>I’ve also had time to make allies and enemies both, the latter of which have become hungry for vengeance and can call upon demons and worse, and won’t rest until they see me destroyed.</p> <p>Yet amid these threats lies the opportunity to gain wealth, power, and influence, and I intend to claim all three.</p> <p>Because I am the Rift Magus still, and I will rise once again, shattering any obstacle in my way.</p> <p><b>I’ve done it before.</b></p> <p><b>I’m already doing it again.</b></p>"; 
